# ğŸ”— URL Shortener

A simple and efficient URL Shortener built using Flask and SQLite as part of my Backend Developer Internship.  
This application converts long URLs into short, shareable links and redirects users to the original URL seamlessly.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Flask-based backend
- REST API to shorten URLs (`POST /shorten`)
- SQLite database for URL storage
- Unique alphanumeric short code generation
- Automatic redirection using short URLs
- Clean and responsive frontend (HTML & CSS)

